date-released: "2026-04-02"

abstract: |
  Bangkong is a production-ready LLM training system featuring Pre-Intelligent 
  Initialization that creates language models with structured prior knowledge 
  embedded at initialization time. This approach achieves 40% reduction in 
  required training tokens compared to standard initialization, validated on 
  consumer hardware (Intel Q8400, 8GB RAM).

